o fade back"},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.essilorpro.com/resources/transitions/transitions-gen-s#legal","children":[{"type":"text","text":"³"}]}],[{"type":"text","text":"Only 25 seconds to sunglasses dark "}],[{"type":"text","text":"The fastest dark lens"},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.essilorpro.com/resources/transitions/transitions-gen-s#legal","children":[{"type":"text","text":"⁵"}]}]]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"With Transitions GEN S, express yourself with endless pairing possibilities."}]}]},{"type":"image","src":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/890593_88fd7b9f0f1548c39bde684500b3f5b9~mv2.png","alt":""},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"items":[[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Widest range on the market: 8 vibrant colors"}]}],[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"New addition to the portfolio: the Ruby color"}]}],[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Better color consistency at all stages"}]},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.essilorpro.com/resources/transitions/transitions-gen-s#legal","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"⁶"}]}]}],[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Endless pairing possibilities"}]}]]},{"type":"image","src":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/890593_57453640fd2d43ed9149fc7742908311~mv2.png","alt":""},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"emphasis","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Transitions GEN S"}]},{"type":"text","text":" is available in 8 exclusive colors, including a brand-new addition: "},{"type":"emphasis","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Transitions GEN S"}]},{"type":"text","text":" Ruby."},{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":" All colors have been optimized to be true to tone at all times, offering vibrant tints regardless of the light or environment."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"While being fully clear indoors, and beautifully colored outdoors, Transitions GEN S provides endless possibilities of pairing to complement any look."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"With Transitions GEN S, experience a better vision quality, faster."}]},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.essilorpro.com/resources/transitions/transitions-gen-s#legal","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"⁹"}]}]}]},{"type":"image","src":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/890593_1fbf960137b94adbbef599da25a55fa3~mv2.png","alt":""},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"items":[[{"type":"text","text":"39% faster vision recovery from intense bright lights vs. clear lenses"},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.essilorpro.com/resources/transitions/transitions-gen-s#legal","children":[{"type":"text","text":"⁷*"}]}],[{"type":"text","text":"40% faster vision recovery during fadeback vs. previous generation"},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.essilorpro.com/resources/transitions/transitions-gen-s#legal","children":[{"type":"text","text":"⁸*"}]}],[{"type":"text","text":"39.5% improved contrast sensitivity during fadeback vs. previous generation"},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.essilorpro.com/resources/transitions/transitions-gen-s#legal","children":[{"type":"text","text":"⁸*"}]}]]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Our groundbreaking technology has been developed with one ambition in mind: uncompromised performance."}]}]},{"type":"image","src":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/890593_a5e03d24cd134a92b72ced57fbc9db24~mv2.png","alt":""},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"items":[[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Proprietary & patented technology"}]}],[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"30 years of photochromic expertise"}]}],[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"100,000 lenses tested"}]}],[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"1,500 new photochromic dyes created"}]}],[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"120 dedicated scientists"}]}]]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"emphasis","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Transitions® GEN S™"}]}]},{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":" uses advanced symbiotic technology where the dyes and matrix are specifically designed to seamlessly interact together. The new matrix architecture strikes the right balance between soft and hard spaces, facilitating dye performance while maintaining robustness. The new super-charged dyes absorb more energy, improving the kinetics inside the matrix and providing the right balance between vivid colors and seamless responsiveness."}]}]},{"type":"image","src":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/890593_9fff3d37b26c4467aa1c4dd39b6f0d64~mv2.png","alt":""},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Resources"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"*Tests carried out on gray lenses. Photochromic performance may vary across colors and lens materials and is influenced by temperature and UV exposure."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"1 93% want or are interested in lenses that enhance their vision beyond vision correction. Transitions Optical, Consumer study on the link between Vision & Protection, external research agency, (CAWI), U.S., Q4 2021, N= 1,000."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"2 For gray polycarbonate & CR39 lenses with a premium anti-reflective coating fading back to 70% transmission @ 23°C."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"3 For gray polycarbonate & CR39 lenses fading back to 70% transmission @ 23°C, compared to the previous generation."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"4 For gray polycarbonate & CR39 lenses achieving 18% transmission @ 23°C."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"5 Compared to gray lenses in the clear to dark (category 3) photochromic category. Transitions GEN S Gray lenses fade back faster to 70% transmission while achieving less than 14% transmission when activated at @ 23°C."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"6 For gray polycarbonate lenses, compared to the previous generation."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"7 Compared to clear lenses. Subject-masked cross-over randomized controlled investigation performed in 2023 on 30 healthy participants (19.2 ± 1.3 years). Testing light stress (discomfort and disability glare, photo-stress recovery) with the clear and darkest states of Transitions GEN S Gray 1.6 index lenses with a premium anti-reflective coating compared to clear 1.6 index lenses with a premium anti-reflective coating. Principal investigator Prof Billy R. Hammond."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"8 Compared to the previous generation. Subject-masked cross-over randomized controlled investigation performed in 2023 on 10 healthy pre-trained participants (29.5 ± 4.0 years). Testing contrast sensitivity during fadeback with Transitions GENS Gray1.6 index lenses with a premium anti-reflective coating compared to Transitions Signature GEN 8 Gray 1.6 index lenses with a premium anti-reflective coating. Principal investigator Prof Pablo Artal. Accepted abstract at ARVO 2024. Duarte-Toledo R, Mompeán J et al., A new photochromic lens improves contrast sensitivity during fadeback."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"9 Vision quality improved in challenging light conditions, notably in bright to very bright light situations. Compared to clear lenses. Subject-masked cross-over randomized controlled investigation performed in 2023 on 30 healthy participants (19.2±1.3years). Testing light stress (discomfort and disability glare, photo-stress recovery) with the clear and darkest states of Transitions GEN S Gray 1.6 index lenses with a premium anti-reflective coating compared to clear 1.6 index lenses with a premium anti-reflective coating. Principal investigator Prof Billy R. Hammond. Vision quality improved in challenging light conditions, notably when moving from a bright to a darker environment. Compared to the previous generation. Subject-masked cross-over randomized controlled investigation performed in 2023 on 10 healthy pre-trained participants (29.5 ± 4.0 years). Testing contrast sensitivity during fadeback with Transitions GEN S Gray 1.6 index lenses with a premium anti-reflective coating compared to Transitions Signature GEN8 Gray1.6 index lenses with a premium anti-reflective coating. Principal investigator Prof Pablo Artal. Accepted abstract at ARVO2024. Duarte-Toledo R, Mompeán J et al., A new photochromic lens improves contrast sensitivity during fadeback."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"10 After seven days of trail per lens type, 86% of wearers chose to keep Transitions GEN S, 5% of wearers chose to keep Transitions Signature GEN 8, and 9% of wearers chose to keep the premium clear lenses. Source: Wearers Test conducted by an external market research agency in the U.S. in Q1 2023 with 134 prescription lens wearers wearing 1.67 index lenses with a premium anti-reflective coating in clear, Transitions GEN S Gray and Transitions Signature GEN 8 Gray."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"©2024 Transitions Optical Limited.  "}]},{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"emphasis","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Transitions "}]}]},{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text