ave, not only on our lives but on the vibrant mosaic that is the Caribbean."}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Stay posted for the next post in the series - "},{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Personalized Care: The Local Advantage in Eyecare"}]}]}]}'::jsonb,
